Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.20,0:03:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总觉得...看起来好成熟唷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.80,0:03:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
