Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪怪的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.28,0:03:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该说是“见内”，还是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.18,0:03:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该是“见外”吧...?
