Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.22,0:03:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那算什么?家里闹分居吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该是吧~?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.43,0:03:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有那回事吧?都到了C不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.26,0:03:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
