Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和莉采儿做ABC的“C”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什...什...什么~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁啊!是谁这样说的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.61,0:07:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有谁...莉采儿自己讲的啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.24,0:07:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.97,0:07:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听好了!那件事完全是子虚乌有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.68,0:07:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是什么也没能做啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.31,0:07:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是说...其实是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不、不要胡乱推测啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.32,0:07:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之，不要再给我乱散布谣言了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是大家都知道了喔\N你看...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.82,0:07:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩城同学马上就被取了\N“色狼纪”的绰号呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.83,0:07:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么我要被人家这样叫不可啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.20,0:07:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为...对啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.13,0:07:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里有对啊 那家伙真是的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.33,0:07:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦~?\N要拿这个出去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.84,0:07:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大剌剌的说什么\N男人味是他的特色...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.34,0:08:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人啊，根本就是事情办完\N马上变个样的随便家伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.34,0:08:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把话说的信誓旦旦...\N什么天使!什么观音娘娘!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.21,0:08:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你要这样\N我也会毫不留情斩断这段情!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可...可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有什么可是不可是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.29,0:08:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照我说的话做，有不对过的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.09,0:08:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.09,0:08:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对会变成“没说分明都是我不对\N该做的都会做，我们和好吧!”的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.73,0:08:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要问可是该怎么做才好，对吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白，我很明白的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿去 照这张小抄上面的说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.97,0:08:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会绝对安全、完美无缺\N盛极必衰、风雨不断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.24,0:08:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好~去吧~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要来我家...?
