Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.33,0:09:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个...那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这个~怎么样啊!
