Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.59,0:09:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.59,0:09:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看...看不懂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃...呃...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.59,0:09:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家很喜欢老公\N也用自己的方式去努力...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.73,0:09:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是老公你最近该怎么说呢\N是冷淡还是不理人家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.50,0:09:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者该说是躲着人家...\N总之你根本就不肯理人家
