Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.39,0:09:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，够了够了!\N那我就如你愿帮你签名吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.39,0:09:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
